title: David Zaffiro Discography 1989-1994 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
DAVID ZAFFIRO DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 1989 - The Other Side
 * 1990 - In Scarlet Storm
 * 1992 - Surrender Absolute
 * 1994 - Yesterday's Left Behind

David Zaffiro is a guitarist, singer, and record producer. His professional career began as guitarist for the metal band Bloodgood. Though he officially left the band following their third album, he did play various parts on later albums. He then began producing records independently and for others. Artists that he has worked with include Acquire the Fire, Andy Chrisman, A Worship House, Brett Williams, Broken Silence, Eli, End Time Warriors, Holy Soldier, Julie Miller, Kate Miner, Kim Hill, Little Big Town, The Passion Worship Band, Paul Q-Pek, Point of Grace, Whitecross, Zion.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
